You can run these demo scripts to apply the changes you need to this repo during a demo instead of editing the files manually.

Run the scripts in order to run each step of the demo.

01-demo-prep.sh - prepares the demo and reminds you of which commands to run in another CLI window for the port-forwards
02-make-dev-change.sh - makes edits to the files ready to build a new container
03-post-demo-revert.sh - reverts the file edits to reset the demo
